Task 1	shell.h, main.c, builtin.c
Task 2	parser.c, executor.c, utils.c, history.c
Task 3	variables.c, signals.c, error_handling.c
Task 4	builtin.c (Modify exit function)
Task 5	builtin.c (Implement env function)
Task 6	main.c (Implement custom getline function)
Task 7	parser.c (Implement custom strtok function)
Task 8	builtin.c (Modify exit function to handle arguments)
Task 9	builtin.c (Implement setenv and unsetenv functions)
Task 10	builtin.c (Implement cd function), variables.c (Update PWD)
Task 11	parser.c (Handle commands separator)
Task 12	parser.c (Handle && and
Task 13	builtin.c (Implement alias function)
Task 14	variables.c (Handle $? and $$ variables)
Task 15	parser.c (Handle comments)
Task 16	main.c (Read and execute commands from a file)
